Package: indi-sx
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libindi1
conflicts: firmware-ccd
replaces: firmware-ccd
Description: INDI Starlight Xpress CCD and Filter Wheel driver.
 Driver for Startlight XPress CCD and Filter Wheel.
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.
 
Package: indi-sx-dbg
Priority: extra
Section: debug
Architecture: any
Depends: indi-sx (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: INDI Starlight Xpress CCD and Filter Wheel driver.
 Driver for Startlight XPress CCD and Filter Wheel.
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.
 This package contains the debug symbols for the this driver, useful to investigate problems in INDI.
